Lambda Test

Create Lambda Function:

    1- Select a Lambda "blueprint" that fits your needs

    2- Configure the function
        - Give name
        - Edit runtime (if need)

    3- Lambda function Code
        - Enter/Edit tje code you want to execute

    4- Lambda Function handler and role
        -At the very least you need to give your function a role

    5- Advanced Settings
        - Allocate memory
        - Run Lambda inside a VPC
        - Encrypt variables (AWS KMS - Key Manager Service)
    
Executing Lambda Function:

    1- Select function > Test

    2- Enter a "test event"

    3- Save & Test

https://docs.aws.amazon.com/lambda/latest/dg/getting-started.html